{"id":594107,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/【图说天朝】跟习主席走-听习主席话/","date":"2018-08-27T02:24:19Z","modified":"2018-08-27T02:24:52Z","title":"【图说天朝】听习主席话 跟习主席走","content":"<p>8月6日，头条号“军营最一线”报道了新疆军区某工兵团家属受邀参与“军官晋职晋衔仪式”。本是一条“正能量词句”滥用的普通军媒稿件，<a href=\"https://www.toutiao.com/i6586527617082475016/?wxshare_count=3&amp;from=timeline&amp;pbid=6593948991242929667\">消息本身</a>并未引起多大关注。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/军媒.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-594108\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/军媒.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"558\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/军媒.jpg 865w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/军媒-296x300.jpg 296w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/军媒-768x779.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/军媒-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/军媒-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>然而有眼尖网友却发现，在仪式现场却出现了一张标语图，内容为：</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>&#8220;听党话，就听习主席话。跟党走，就跟习主席走&#8221;</strong></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/1533545263313dfd9b51d68.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-594109\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/1533545263313dfd9b51d68.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/1533545263313dfd9b51d68.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/1533545263313dfd9b51d68-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/1533545263313dfd9b51d68-360x240.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[25368,9526,13222,20189,15494,12116]}